ai_summary.en: With Bitcoin's Fear & Greed Index deep in 'Fear' at 29, the overarching crypto market sentiment remains highly cautious. On the institutional ETH chain, whales exhibit a near-neutral to slightly bearish posture, evidenced by significant stablecoin outflows as smart money de-risks. Conversely, the more speculative SOL chain sees mild bullish sentiment and stablecoin inflows, suggesting some retail players are cautiously accumulating, albeit on much lower volume. This divergence, coupled with the macro fear, indicates a challenging environment where any short-term rallies may be limited without broader market conviction.
ai_summary.zh: 随着比特币恐惧与贪婪指数在29（恐惧）区，加密市场整体情绪保持高度谨慎。以太坊链上的机构投资者表现出近乎中性到轻微看跌的立场，稳定币净流出表明智能资金正在去风险。然而，Solana链上的零售投机资金则呈现出温和的看涨情绪和稳定币流入，尽管交易量小得多，暗示有部分资金在谨慎抄底。宏观恐惧与机构去风险的背景下，市场短期内可能面临持续挑战，难以出现强劲反弹。
